-- Nigeria’s Sanusi Says Petroleum Bill to Help Boost Investment
-- B y   A n d r e s   R .   M a r t i n e z
-- 2012-01-27T09:30:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/nigeria-s-sanusi-says-petroleum-bill-to-help-boost-investment.html
Nigeria ’s petroleum bill will boost
investment in the nation’s industries and will create jobs, said
central bank Governor Lamido Sanusi.  The bill, which was recently submitted by the government to
lawmakers, will promote development, he said in an interview
with Bloomberg Television in Davos,  Switzerland , today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
